    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's the look on their faces. i was supposed to be the one who made it, the one who provided everything. now i'm just a liability. everything i touch just turns to nothing. i feel like i've already died inside, so why does it even matter if the rest of me catches up?",
